model: Aventador LP700-4 "Azur Lane" by Falcon Car Rental Los Angeles
collection: The Last of Beta BM Collection
description: During the AX2019, this Aventador was on display at the official Azur Lane stand. The livery showcased various in-game race queen skins, those being Atago - Stunning Speedster (right door), Takao - Full Throttle Charmer (left door), Duke of York - Prestige of the Glorious Formula (front end. left) and Prince of Wales - The Laureate's Victory Lap (front end, right). The attention the car grabbed eventually paved the way for the itashas shown during the 5th Anniversary Livestream in August 2023, but that's a different story now...
creator: Lemon
